The story is about an astronaut, a life support technician, an energetic comic, and a committed rabble-rouser. It starts in an ocean empire on an arid world artificially
created by magic. The story begins with a pleasant surprise, climaxes with a trial, and ends with an accident while traveling. The speed of technological
advancement is a major part of this story.

This is a road-trip story with a focus on happiness and how people can't beat the odds. The story is about a disloyal nun who hates an incoherent champion.
It starts in a large city in Australia. The fact that space may be the last frontier is a major part of this story.
